>> source: https://recipe.awesomedrinks.com/recipe/banana-daiquiri/

Cut and peal @banana{1/2}, add banana, @dark rum{45%ml}, @fresh lime juice{15%ml}, @simple syrup{15%ml}, @triple sec{15%ml} and @ice{5%cubes} into #blender and blend for ~{10%seconds} or until smooth.

Strain into a #Nick & Nora glass{} and serve.

-- Use your favorite rum for this drink, it makes a difference.
